parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can increase the risk of serious injury or death to the occupants.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in a crash
occupants sustain injuries due to lack of airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt to restrain the occupant can increase the risk of serious injury or death in a crash.
symptoms: Seatbelt does not catch or restrain the occupant
occupant is thrown into the steering wheel or other parts of the vehicle.
